t could be that I use documents between Office 2007 on a PC and 2008 on a Mac, but shouldn't there be 100% compatibility. Perhaps the 2011 version will be better, but for the time being, this is the single most frustrating piece of software I currently have on my iMac, primarily because I know how well it works on the PC side.  I'm not one given to conspiracy theories, but I just can't help but shake the feeling that Microsoft didn't put their best and rightest on this "Mac" project. :(	-1
